Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切斯特 请求轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发送位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要去死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿耳戈斯小队及达卡基地部队与飞行者接触
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(333,655)}Argos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(883,655)}Aviator
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿耳戈斯小队受到了毁灭性打击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便可以向它给情报让它转移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但控制不了它的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火速重整部队 让他们追击将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主型怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以回收的机体为基础 就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 驾驶员会被同化是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还是需要D岛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就动用傀儡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(700,655)}puppet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果强行使用 他们的人格会被摧毁的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他们就是弃子 正确使用才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把怪物们集中到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了人类 要消灭地面的Mir
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.46,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(500,500)\fs26\pos(839,141)}第21回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.46,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(500,500)\pos(1063,141)}觉醒的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里原来其实也是陆地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同陆地一并沉没的国家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命…并不是全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个护身符 里面写了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望广登没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一杯咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你在开枪杀我之前喝上一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这么想 我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恨我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是执行了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要…到龙宫岛来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看看我们的故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从天上看的话 根本没法知道你要破坏的是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说那是个美丽的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意让我去 我也想亲眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抑制剂也剩得不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人在山那头 不用强行出击也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为什么在被人类追杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援军什么时候会来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地真的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一直在到处流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信通识者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和牵牛联络上 世界就会拥护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和比利都很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回过神来发现就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然早了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和剑司说好成人礼的时候要帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}注：日本是以20岁算成年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是帮我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20岁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次开上法芙娜的时候是14岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想更慢点变成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真正的和平到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界一定会变成你说的那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你跟我说要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我以为自己已经不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 回到我们的岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被感谢的人总是他啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么啊 你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不像总士前辈这样打算退出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知故问 我说远见前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不争这个了 别打扰他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你确定这样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是让我冲出去搅局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是很明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北上之后怀有敌意的群体就越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果兵力不足 连运输机都不能起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就亲自上阵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你一把年纪还真的能开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一我出事 就拜托你指挥部队了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活到最后是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是 我们必须保证希望活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:56.70,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1600,0)}N第20营地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第20营地 我们启动了Mk.Sein与Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄们在为我们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员迅速过桥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10点钟方向出现大量敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员开始迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北极决战过去5年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum的憎恨倾泻到我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.26,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,N第21营地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个群体都对我们恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么努力跟他说话了 他还不来帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续呼唤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:55.28,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}N第23营地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过隔离壁一个月之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抑制剂耗尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要驾驶法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必定会受到同化现象的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 其末期症状显现了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员短缺 于是我们征召了预备役
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也全部牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 许多人停止了前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法通讯 他们脱离了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然主动去当敌人的诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过隔离壁40天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅有8架的运输机之一坠毁的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.85,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,N第29营地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熬过了战斗的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力尽于饥寒交迫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.08,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,N第30营地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦睡着 可能就是永眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一心祈祷 但愿在下一天仍然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过隔离壁56天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号源就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发出应答信号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是过去的求援信号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龙宫岛的飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛通告同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 龙宫岛通告同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正前往与各位会合的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还有这种事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因可能遭到敌人的监听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无法与各位直接通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相信诸位能够抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位相信 我们就在你们所要前往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能回岛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么会知道我们会到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据奥尔嘉带到的消息推测出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——虽然这不可能 但也想不出别的可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的声音也能传到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会传到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我们抵达了陆地的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5027名幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6架运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15部法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是付出1万7千人的牺牲所换来的一切
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到应答信号 距离约50单位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D岛就在海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃编队控制室及车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将Mir和人员送上运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆战机从海里前进 向D岛进发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面就是岛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天吧 11月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了就和岛上的人一起庆祝一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到敌人的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫长的旅途也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我彻底明白了 光靠战斗是成不了希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是付出生命的话 将到达不了任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有创造新和平的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护引导世界的人们 保护对话的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了所有牺牲的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们隐藏了敌意？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（插曲）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿撒谢尔型…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人！港口那边又出现了一只！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我去 总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是请求 直接就是命令了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我撑到援军到达！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命留存到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把周围都冻上了…是为了在海中维持同化能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 难得撑到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3点钟方向有对空导弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护运输机！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉醒的时候到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了啊 D岛的法芙娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖！不能过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的 飞不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们大家合为一体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘！拜托了 回个话！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾 向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心…要被夺走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开枪 拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的同化…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！你快脱离！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！我下不了手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也敢朝你们开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在这种时候…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晖 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混帐！放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的敌人居然是人类么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔 启动认证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔特先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！这家伙想自爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 放手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想看看你们的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化现象…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…连我身上也出现了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上又来一只？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点！要沉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运输机和法芙娜都掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这上面的都是人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们和Festum有什么两样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 这下完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的声音传到了 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他出生了我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的天空
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（ED）
